{"tid":1702382,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"仗前，先振軍心。","createTime":"2019-11-09T16:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T04:06:03.000Z","uid":136591,"like":626,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"f8e9154916dca679d793b81cb46910a8b4ff4a20","tid":1702382,"uid":136591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:08:19.000Z","msg":"五個月既抗爭之路，大家一齊走過。<br />\n當中士氣有高漲，有低落。<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">大家都好叻</span></strong>，一齊走過當中高高低低。<br />\n大家回想下，自己既付出：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">老年人</span></strong>：相信各公公婆婆都心痛學生，不少晚上睇住電視而流淚。更身體力行落街抗爭。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">大人</span></strong>：心痛學生，憤而出錢支援學生，落街屌狗，更甚用自己地位、職業去發聲。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">年青人</span></strong>：以血肉之軀抵抗政權，被家人踢出家門、放低學業、係前線擋子彈、食煙食椒、係狗屋被毒打、被強姦。<br />\n<br />\n首先，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好多謝大家一路並肩作戰</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n數之不盡既<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">手足被捕、被打、被斬、被彈傷、被自殺、被浮屍、被送中、被姦。</span></strong><br />\n更有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">數位手足放低遺願，先走一步。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">這時這刻，大家憤怒、震怒。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">周同學既遇害，女手足既被強姦。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">我們永不忘記！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">曙光來了。</span>因為全民憤怒。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">夫戰，勇氣也。</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">讓憤怒化作勇氣。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">政府害怕了。</span></strong>近日與警察慢慢割席。<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>警察害怕了。</strong></span>近日與前線慢慢割席。<br />\n他們害怕的，是我們香港人民。<br />\n<br />\n共匪游擊專家，毛澤東所言：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「敵疲我打，敵退我追」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n機會來了。大家要好好把握。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各路同志，珍重。</span></span><br />\n明天，後天。將來。以港人之名，重奪香港。<br />\n同行兒女，一起光復香港。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/od4FWXv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fod4FWXv.jpg&h=90120750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CoZ3ahw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCoZ3ahw.png&h=24b72a8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"89105171d585930b7a10ef0b4a985b6f92c3f2b3","tid":1702382,"uid":136591,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:09:20.000Z","msg":"「夫戰，勇氣也，一鼓作氣，再而衰，三而竭。」"},{"pid":"5e389414dce6f4c8c11a3443dac0778d409e54f6","tid":1702382,"uid":265917,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:10:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>想多啲人參與擺工？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">小妹發現facebook好少行動文宣流通 <br />\n同埋好少係街收到airdrop既文宣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>要記住嚟場革命唔係淨係屬於連登仔<br />\n四五十歲既人多數淨係上fb 佢地多數只會認同大眾都吹奏緊既野</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我地有咩可以做？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>正所謂「識睇一定睇comment」<br />\n1）我地要多啲係唔同post下面貼行動文宣同出下發夢注意事項post<br />\n2）仲有要係街不斷airdrop啲文宣俾人</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>零成本 你唔係唔做呀嘛</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"be81024777d8a67a6adf2679af6247e3fdad14b8","tid":1702382,"uid":282891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b78a909d71dab058495a3672fbe9f8d1181eb4","tid":1702382,"uid":101307,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:10:56.000Z","msg":"你二樓個句野其實已經唔岩用 而家變左長期戰<br />\n但同意要追擊"},{"pid":"6abf0dd5acf9a859d1e7878743d2adb1ae06dbea","tid":1702382,"uid":136591,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:12:03.000Z","msg":"樓下請以激昂打氣說話回覆，以作振奮。"},{"pid":"8b3402a592d8161b90f64b45cddee2b8aba6bfaf","tid":1702382,"uid":136591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3b78a909d71dab058495a3672fbe9f8d1181eb4","tid":1702382,"uid":101307,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:10:56.000Z","msg":"你二樓個句野其實已經唔岩用 而家變左長期戰<br />\n但同意要追擊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:12:43.000Z","msg":"今次係追擊既曙光。<br />\n各位努力。"},{"pid":"f221281700ffaad7d13c7cf8d151db6a3ba09175","tid":1702382,"uid":136591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:13:17.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"f338d65e34b2cf0aa630e3830f9afd816f31f69a","tid":1702382,"uid":136591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f221281700ffaad7d13c7cf8d151db6a3ba09175","tid":1702382,"uid":136591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:13:17.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:13:27.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"ba99220197e0ad70f58cd8eb8f98f990943e82a1","tid":1702382,"uid":158877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:16:48.000Z","msg":"11大三罷 用噴漆噴巴士倒後鏡<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1702367\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1702367</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n成本極企 安全性高 速度快過set rb<br />\n事後可清潔 就算要賠錢都大把人賠"},{"pid":"af54482fdae6e15b1da6dbe3db402400a8ef3b85","tid":1702382,"uid":136591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:18:12.000Z","msg":"香港人，加油。"},{"pid":"1c3